    "## 8. Understanding the Algorithm\n",
    "\n",
    "### 8.1 Why is this efficient?\n",
    "\n",
    "| Approach | Complexity | Parallelizable | GPU Friendly |\n",
    "|-----------|------------|----------------|--------------|\n",
    "| Sequential | O(n) | ❌ | ❌ |\n",
    "| Parallel Scan | O(log n) | ✅ | ✅ |\n",
    "\n",
    "### 8.2 Key Insight\n",
    "\n",
    "The parallel scan exploits the **associativity** of the SSM recurrence:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$(a \\oplus b) \\oplus c = a \\oplus (b \\oplus c)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "This allows us to compute **chunks** in parallel and then **combine** them.\n",
    "\n",
    "### 8.3 Practical Notes\n",
    "\n",
    "- In practice, efficient implementations use **CUDA kernels** for the scan\n",
    "- The **Mamba** paper uses a specialized **HIPARA** (hybrid parallel recurrent) algorithm\n",
    "- Some implementations fuse the scan with discretization for efficiency"
   ]
