    "\n",
    "**Key Takeaways**:\n",
    "1. ✅ Sequential SSM is O(n) - slow on long sequences\n",
    "2. ✅ Parallel scan reduces to O(log n) using associativity\n",
    "3. ✅ The key is reformulating SSM as an associative scan\n",
    "4. ✅ GPU utilization is much better with parallel scan\n",
